com.android.car.internal.util

注释类型 DataClass

public @interface DataClass

    • 元素详细资料

      • genParcelable

        public abstract boolean genParcelable
        Generates Parcelable#writeToParcel, Parcelable#describeContents and a Parcelable.Creator. Can be implicitly requested by adding "implements Parcelable" to class signature You can provide custom parceling logic by using a DataClass.ParcelWith annotation with a custom Parcelling subclass. Alternatively, for one-off customizations you can declare methods like: void parcelFieldName(Parcel dest, int flags) static FieldType unparcelFieldName(Parcel in)
        默认值:
        false

      • genAidl

        public abstract boolean genAidl
        Generates a simple "parcelable" .aidl file alongside the original .java file If not explicitly requested/suppressed, is on iff genParcelable() is on
        默认值:
        false

      • genGetters

        public abstract boolean genGetters
        Generates getters for each field. You can request for getter to lazily initialize your field by declaring a method like: FieldType lazyInitFieldName() You can request for the lazy initialization to be thread safe my marking the field volatile.
        默认值:
        true

      • genHiddenGetters

        public abstract boolean genHiddenGetters
        genGetters() with @hide
        默认值:
        false

      • genSetters

        public abstract boolean genSetters
        Generates setters for each field.
        默认值:
        false

      • genHiddenSetters

        public abstract boolean genHiddenSetters
        genSetters() with @hide
        默认值:
        false

      • genConstructor

        public abstract boolean genConstructor
        Generates a public constructor with each field initialized from a parameter and optionally some user-defined state validation at the end. Uses field nullability/default value presence to determine optional parameters. Requesting a genBuilder() suppresses public constructor generation by default. You receive a callback at the end of constructor call by declaring the method: void onConstructed() This is the place to put any custom validation logic.
        默认值:
        true

      • genHiddenConstructor

        public abstract boolean genHiddenConstructor
        genConstructor() with @hide
        默认值:
        false

      • genBuilder

        public abstract boolean genBuilder
        Generates a Builder for your class. Uses a package-private constructor under the hood, so same rules hold as for genConstructor()
        默认值:
        false

      • genHiddenBuilder

        public abstract boolean genHiddenBuilder
        genBuilder() with @hide
        默认值:
        false

      • genEqualsHashCode

        public abstract boolean genEqualsHashCode
        Generates a structural Object.equals(java.lang.Object) + Object.hashCode(). You can customize individual fields' logic by declaring methods like: fieldNameEquals(ClassName otherInstance) fieldNameEquals(FieldType otherValue) fieldNameHashCode()
        默认值:
        false

      • genToString

        public abstract boolean genToString
        Generates a structural Object.toString(). You can customize individual fields' logic by declaring methods like: fieldNameToString()
        默认值:
        false

      • genForEachField

        public abstract boolean genForEachField
        Generates a utility method that takes a per-field callback and calls it once for each field with its name and value. If some fields are of primitive types, and additional overload is generated that takes multiple callbacks, specialized for used primitive types to avoid auto-boxing, e.g. DataClass.PerIntFieldAction.
        默认值:
        false

      • genCopyConstructor

        public abstract boolean genCopyConstructor
        Generates a constructor that copies the given instance of the same class.
        默认值:
        false

      • genHiddenCopyConstructor

        public abstract boolean genHiddenCopyConstructor
        genCopyConstructor() with @hide
        默认值:
        false

      • genConstDefs

        public abstract boolean genConstDefs
        Generates constant annotations(IntDef/StringDef) for any constant groups with common prefix. The annotation names are based on the common prefix. For int constants this additionally generates the corresponding static *ToString method and uses it in Object.toString(). Additionally, any fields you annotate with the generated constants will be automatically validated in constructor. Int constants specified as hex(0x..) are considered to be flags, which is taken into account for in their *ToString and validation. You can optionally override the name of the generated annotation by annotating each constant with the desired annotation name. Unless suppressed, is implied by presence of constants with common prefix.
        默认值:
        true

      • genHiddenConstDefs

        public abstract boolean genHiddenConstDefs
        genConstDefs() with @hide
        默认值:
        false
